OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, frequent and
OL,7,Fprolonged in places, with
OL,8,Fthunderstorms possible in northern
OL,9,Fcounties. Further showers overnight
OL,10,Fmixed with clear spells, before
OL,11,Fperhaps turning more generally wet by
OL,12,Fthe morning. Breezy at times and
OL,13,Fstaying relatively mild.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FA wet start for many, then
OL,16,Fbrighter with scattered heavy and
OL,17,Flocally thundery showers. A rather
OL,18,Fcool and blustery day but warm when
OL,19,Fthe sunshine comes out and in shelter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
