OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMuch
OL,6,Fdrier on Friday with sunny intervals,
OL,7,Fbut isolated showers remain possible.
OL,8,FRather windy and changeable over the
OL,9,Fweekend with rain or showers, mainly
OL,10,Fon Saturday. Warm in any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
